#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:45
#, no-c-format
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "Uvod"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:52
#, no-c-format
msgid "Launching &kfind;"
msgstr "Pokretanje &kfind;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:54
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The Find Files tool is a useful method of searching for specific files on "
"your computer, or for searching for files that match a pattern. An example "
"of this could include searching for files of a particular type or with "
"certain letters in the filename. You can load this utility in &konqueror; "
"(in file manager mode) by selecting <menuchoice><shortcut><keycombo action="
"\"simul\">&Ctrl; <keycap>F</keycap></keycombo></shortcut><guimenu>Tools</"
"guimenu> <guimenuitem>Find File</guimenuitem></menuchoice> from the menu. If "
"you want to use &kfind; as a standalone search tool, launch it by using "
"&krunner;."
msgstr ""
"Alat za pronalazak datoteka je koristan metod za pretraživanje specifičnih "
"datoteka na vašem računaru, ili za pretraživanje datoteka koje odgovaraju "
"uzorku. Primjer za ovo uključuje pretraživanje datoteka posebnog tipa ili sa "
"određenim slovima u nazivu. Možete učitati ovaj alat u &konqueror; (u režimu "
"file manager) označavanjem <menuchoice><shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul"
"\">&Ctrl; <keycap>F</keycap></keycombo></shortcut><guimenu>Alati</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Pronađi datoteku</guimenuitem></menuchoice> iz izbornika. Ako "
"želite koristiti &kfind; kao samostalni alat za pretraživanje, pokrenite ga "
"koristeći &krunner;."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:71
#, no-c-format
msgid "Finding Files"
msgstr "Pronalaženje datoteka"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:74
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Name/Location Tab"
msgstr "Ime/Lokacija tabulator"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:76
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When starting &kfind;, you will see a quite simple window. Type in the name "
"of the file you are searching for in the text box labeled <guilabel>Named:</"
"guilabel>. You can use wildcard matching and a semicolon (<quote>;</quote>) "
"for separating multiple names."
msgstr ""
"Pri pokretanju &kfind; vidjet ćete prilično jednostavan prozor. Otkucajte "
"ime datoteke koju tražite u tekstualnom prozoru pod nazivom "
"<guilabel>Nazvano:</guilabel>. Možete koristiti zamjenske znakove i tačku-"
"zarez (<quote>;</quote>) za razdvajanje višestrukih imena."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:81
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Choose a folder where you want to search by typing it in the field "
"<guilabel>Look in:</guilabel> or by clicking <guibutton>Browse...</"
"guibutton> (you can toggle the display of the hidden files and folder in the "
"dialog using the shortcuts <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;<keycap>.</"
"keycap></keycombo> or <keycap>F8</keycap>) and press &Enter; or click the "
"<guibutton>Find</guibutton> button. Use the <guibutton>Stop</guibutton> "
"button to cancel a search. A search result can be saved in &HTML; format or "
"as plain text with the <guibutton>Save As...</guibutton> button."
msgstr ""
"Odaberite folder gdje želite pretraživati kucanjem u polje "
"<guilabel>Pogledaj u:</guilabel> ili klikom na<guibutton>Pretraži...</"
"guibutton> (možete preklopiti zaslon sakrivenih datoteka i foldera u "
"dijalogu korištenjem prečica <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;<keycap>.</"
"keycap></keycombo> ili <keycap>F8</keycap>) i pritiskom na &Enter; ili "
"klikom na  <guibutton>Pronađi</guibutton>. Koristite <guibutton>Zaustavi</"
"guibutton> da prekinete pretraživanje. Rezultat pretraživanja može biti "
"snimljen u &HTML; formatu ili kao običan tekst sa <guibutton>Snimi kao...</"
"guibutton> dugmetom."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:90
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If <guilabel>Include subfolders</guilabel> is checked all subfolders "
"starting from your chosen folder will be searched too. If you enable "
"<guilabel>Case sensitive search</guilabel>, &kfind; will only find files "
"with the exact case matching names. Enable the option <guilabel>Show hidden "
"files</guilabel> to include them in your search. Selecting <guilabel>Use "
"files index</guilabel> lets you use the files' index created by the "
"<quote>locate</quote> package to speed-up the search."
msgstr ""
"Ako je <guilabel>Uključi podfoldere</guilabel> označen, svi podfolderi, "
"počev od vašeg odabranog foldera, će se pretraživati. Ako omogućite "
"<guilabel>Pretraga velikih i malih slova</guilabel>, &kfind; će pronaći samo "
"datoteke sa tačnim podudaranjem imena. Omogućite opciju <guilabel>Prikaži "
"skrivene datoteke</guilabel> da biste uključili i njih u svoju pretragu. "
"Označavanje <guilabel>Koristi indeks datoteka</guilabel> dopušta vam da "
"koristite indeks datoteka kreiranih pomoću <quote>lociraj</quote> paketa da "
"bi se ubrzalo pretraživanje."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:100
#, no-c-format
msgid "You can use the following wildcards for file or folder names:"
msgstr ""
"Možete koristiti slijedeće zamjenske znakove za imena datoteka ili foldera:"

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:106
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Asterisk <quote><keycap>*</keycap></quote>"
msgstr "Zvjezdica <quote><keycap>*</keycap></quote>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:108
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The asterisk stands for any number of missing characters (even zero), that "
"means &eg; searching for <userinput>marc*</userinput> may find the files "
"<filename>marc</filename>, <filename>marc.png</filename> and <filename> "
"marc_must_not_read_this.kwd</filename>. <userinput>mar*.kwd</userinput> may "
"find <filename>marketplace.kwd</filename> and "
"<filename>marc_must_not_read_this.kwd</filename>."
msgstr ""
"Zvjezdica je napisana umjesto bilo kojeg broja nedostajućih znakova (čak i "
"nula), što znači &eg; potražujući <userinput>marc*</userinput> može pronaći "
"datoteke <filename>marc</filename>, <filename>marc.png</filename> i "
"<filename> marc_must_not_read_this.kwd</filename>. <userinput>mar*.kwd</"
"userinput> može pronaći <filename>marketplace.kwd</filename> i "
"<filename>marc_must_not_read_this.kwd</filename>."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:121
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Question Mark <quote><keycap>?</keycap></quote>"
msgstr "Upitnik <quote><keycap>?</keycap></quote>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:123
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In contrast to the asterisk, the question mark stands for exactly one "
"character, so <userinput>mar?</userinput> will find <filename>marc</"
"filename>, but <userinput>marc?</userinput> will not find anything, as our "
"files are called <filename>marc</filename> and <filename>marc.png</"
"filename>. You can put as many question marks in the term as you want, it "
"will find exactly that number of characters."
msgstr ""
"Nasuprot zvjezdici, upitnik je napisan za samo jedan znak, tako da će "
"<userinput>mar?</userinput> pronaći <filename>marc</filename>, ali "
"<userinput>marc?</userinput> neće pronaći ništa, pošto su naše datoteke "
"nazvane <filename>marc</filename> and <filename>marc.png</filename>. Možete "
"staviti koliko god upitnika želite, u kojem god smislu želite, pronaći će "
"tačno taj broj znakova."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:135
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Character Set <quote>[...]</quote>"
msgstr "Skup znakova <quote>[...]</quote>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:137
#, no-c-format
msgid "This matches any of the characters between the braces."
msgstr "Ovo odgovara bilo kojem od znakova između zagrada."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:145
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Of course you can combine two or more wildcard symbols in a search term."
msgstr ""
"Naravno da možete kombinovati dva ili više zamjenskih znakova u pojmu za "
"pretragu."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:149
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The results of your search will be displayed in the box below. A click with "
"the &RMB; on a selection in this box opens a context menu with a list of "
"actions for the selected files or folders."
msgstr ""
"Rezultati vaše pretrage će biti prikazani u prozoru ispod. Klik sa &RMB; na "
"oznaku u ovom prozoru, otvara izbornik sa listom akcija za označene datoteke "
"ili foldere."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:158
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Contents Tab"
msgstr "Kartica sadržaja"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:162
#, no-c-format
msgid "File type"
msgstr "Tip datoteke"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:164
#, no-c-format
msgid "Here you can specify the type of file you are searching for."
msgstr "Ovdje možete odrediti koju vrstu datoteke tražite."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:171
#, no-c-format
msgid "Containing text"
msgstr "Sadrži tekst"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:173
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Type in the word or phrase the files you are searching for must contain. "
"Note: If you do this in a large folder or checked <guilabel>Include "
"subfolders</guilabel> in the <guilabel>Name/Location</guilabel> tab, this "
"may take a long time."
msgstr ""
"Unesite riječ ili frazu datoteka koje tražite u sadržaj. Napomena: Ako ovo "
"radite u velikom folderu ili sa označenim <guilabel>Uključi podfoldere</"
"guilabel> u <guilabel>Ime/Lokacija</guilabel> kartici, to može potrajati "
"duže vrijeme."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:181
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This option will <emphasis>not</emphasis> work for all files listed under "
"<guilabel>File type</guilabel>. Only the following file types are supported:"
msgstr ""
"Ova opcija <emphasis>neće</emphasis> raditi za sve datoteke navedene ispod "
"<guilabel>Tip datoteke</guilabel>. Samo navedeni tipovi datoteka su podržani:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:185
#, no-c-format
msgid "Text files, &eg; source code and <filename>README</filename> files"
msgstr ""
"Tekstualne datoteke, &eg; izvorni kod i <filename>README</filename> datoteke."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:186
#, no-c-format
msgid "OpenOffice.org Writer / LibreOffice Writer"
msgstr "OpenOffice.org Pisac / LibreOffice Pisac"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:187
#, no-c-format
msgid "OpenOffice.org Impress / LibreOffice Impress"
msgstr "OpenOffice.org Impress / LibreOffice Impress"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:188
#, no-c-format
msgid "OpenOffice.org Calc / LibreOffice Calc"
msgstr "OpenOffice.org Calc / LibreOffice Calc"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:189
#, no-c-format
msgid "Calligra Words"
msgstr "Calligra Words"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:190
#, no-c-format
msgid "Calligra Sheets"
msgstr "Calligra Sheets"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:191
#, no-c-format
msgid "Calligra Stage"
msgstr "Calligra Stage"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:201
#, no-c-format
msgid "Case sensitive"
msgstr "Razlikuj velika i mala slova"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:203
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you enable this option, &kfind; will only find text in files with the "
"exact case matching, &eg; <userinput>MARC</userinput> will only match "
"<quote>MARC</quote>, not <quote>Marc</quote>."
msgstr ""
"Ako omogućite ovu opciju, &kfind; će pronaći samo tekst u datotekama sa "
"tačnim podudaranjem, &eg; <userinput>MARC</userinput> će se podudarati samo "
"sa <quote>MARC</quote>, ne i <quote>Marc</quote>."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:213
#, no-c-format
msgid "Regular expression"
msgstr "Regularan izraz"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:214
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you have installed the &kregexpeditor; tool from playground/utils on the "
"&kde; git server, you will have this additional option. Enabling it will "
"allow you to search for a <firstterm>regexp</firstterm> or regular "
"expression. A regexp is a way to specify conditions for your search, and "
"they can be very complex, and equally they can be very powerful. If you are "
"unfamiliar with regular expressions, you can choose <guibutton>Edit</"
"guibutton> button to open &kregexpeditor;. This tool allows you to construct "
"your set of conditions graphically, and then generates the expression for "
"you."
msgstr ""
"Ako ste instalirali &kregexpeditor; alat sa igraonice/korisnosti na &kde; "
"git server, imat ćete ovu dodatnu opciju. Njenim mogućavanjem ćete moći "
"pretraživati <firstterm>regexp</firstterm> ili regularne izraze. Regexp je "
"način za specificiranje uslova vaše pretrage, koji mogu biti veoma "
"kompleksni, ali ujedno i veoma moćni. Ako vam nisu poznati regularni izrazi, "
"možete odabrati <guibutton>Uredi</guibutton> dugme da biste otvorili "
"&kregexpeditor;. Ovaj alat vam omogućava da izgradite grafički komplet "
"uslova i onda generiše izraze za vas."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:225
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kregexpeditor; is a very useful tool, and can be used from within many "
"&kde; applications other than &kfind;. You can find more information from "
"within its own help file."
msgstr ""
"&kregexpeditor; je veoma koristan alat, i može se koristiti unutar mnogih "
"&kde; aplikacija, osim &kfind;. Možete pronaći više informacija u njegovoj "
"vlastitoj pomoćnoj datoteci."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:231
#, no-c-format
msgid "Include binary files"
msgstr "Uključi binarne datoteke"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:232
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This lets you search in any type of file, even those that usually do not "
"contain text (for example program files and images)."
msgstr ""
"Ovo vam dopušta pretraživanje u bilo kojoj vrsti datoteka, čak i u onoj koja "
"obično ne sadrži tekst (naprimjer, programske datoteke i slike)."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:238
#, no-c-format
msgid "Search metainfo sections"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:240
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"These two fields can be used to search within files' specific comments or "
"metainfo."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:243
#, no-c-format
msgid "Here are some major cases:"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:248
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<emphasis>Video files (avi, mp4, &etc;)</emphasis>: specify some tag "
"(<userinput>Bitrate</userinput>, <userinput>Duration</userinput>, &etc;) and "
"its value to find items which have the specified parameter value in their "
"metadata."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:253
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<emphasis>Images (png, jpeg, &etc;)</emphasis>: specify some tag "
"(<userinput>Width</userinput>, <userinput>Height</userinput>, &etc;) and its "
"value to find items which have the specified parameter value in their "
"metadata."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:258
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<emphasis>Audio files (mp3, flac, &etc;)</emphasis>: specify some tag "
"(<userinput>Title</userinput>, <userinput>Album</userinput>, &etc;) and its "
"value to find items which have the specified parameter value in their "
"metadata."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:263
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<emphasis>Ebooks (epub, azw, fb2, &etc;)</emphasis>: specify some tag "
"(<userinput>Title</userinput>, <userinput>Author</userinput>, &etc;) and its "
"value to find items which have the specified parameter value in their "
"metadata."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:269
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If there is a translation of the tags into your language you can use the "
"localized tag names in the search criterion."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:280
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Properties Tab"
msgstr "Kartica osobina"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:282
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Here you can refine your search. These are the special refinements you can "
"choose:"
msgstr ""
"Ovdje možete suziti svoju pretragu. Ovo su posebna poboljšanja koja možete "
"odabrati:"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:290
#, no-c-format
msgid "Find all files created or modified"
msgstr "Pronađi sve kreirane ili izmijenjene datoteke"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:292
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Here you can either enter two dates, between which the files were created or "
"modified, or specify a time period."
msgstr ""
"Ovdje možete ili ukucati dva datuma, između kojih su datoteke kreirane ili "
"modifikovane, ili navesti vremenski period."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:300
#, no-c-format
msgid "File size is"
msgstr "Veličina datoteke je"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:302
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Here you can specify if the file has to be at least or at most as big as the "
"size you entered in the following box, or else equal to the size."
msgstr ""
"Ovdje možete specificirati da li datoteka ne smije biti manja ili veća od "
"veličine koju ste unijeli u navedeni prozor, ili mora biti jednaka toj "
"veličini."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:310
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Files owned by user</guilabel>, <guilabel>Files owned by group</"
"guilabel>"
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Datoteke u vlasništvu korisnika</guilabel>, <guilabel>Datoteke u "
"vlasništvu grupe</guilabel>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:312
#, no-c-format
msgid "Here you can specify user and group names as owner of the files."
msgstr "Ovdje možete navesti imena korisnika i grupa kao vlasnika datoteka."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:325
#, no-c-format
msgid "Credits and License"
msgstr "Zasluge i licenca"

